{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"03ec455134","title":"在中央人民政府元旦团拜会上的祝词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ee3592956","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"03ec455134","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a8cb497602","type":"title","text":"在中央人民政府元旦团拜会上的祝词","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9679f652e","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们全体——人民政府工作人员，人民志愿军和人民解放军的指挥员、战斗员，各民主党派，各人民团体，各少数民族和全国人民，在各个工作战线上的胜利！","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9791ef8a37","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在抗美援朝战线上的胜利！","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c6c99bb21","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在国防战线上的胜利！","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cb06e1f2f","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们住土地改革战线上的胜利！","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f471612ce9","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在镇压反革命战线上的胜利！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d32676f27","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在经济和财政战线上的胜利！","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c0688ffa3","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在文化和教育战线上的胜利！","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4e4a3b3df","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在社会各界首先是知识分子的思想改造战线上的胜利！","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3da3256b4","type":"paragraph","text":"我还要祝我们在新开辟的一条战线上的胜利，这就是号召我国全体人民和一切工作人员一致起来，大张旗鼓地，雷厉风行地，开展一个大规模的反对贪污、反对浪费、反对官僚主义的斗争，将这些旧社会遗留下来的污毒洗干净！","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98a66d7f27","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，我们在上述一切战线上，在一九五一年，都已取得了胜利，有许多是极其伟大的胜利。我们希望，经过我们的共同努力，所有这些工作，在一九五二年能够取得更大的胜利！","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fe16f8427","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国万岁！","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"499f6ae344","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五二年一月三日）","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"03ec455134","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":50,"end":49}}}},"__N_SSG":true}